settings.description: Go high up in the skies to Boom Boom's Castle high up in the air! (There's a secret e-Coin hidden in the turnips in the Plains and a 3-up moon also on top of the Plains).
Venture through a switch-and-money-filled world of speedrunning, careful timing, precise jumps, and more! There's also an E-Coin up high in space, waiting to be found!
A classic first level from Super Mario Bros from NES
